    "synopsis": "The war for Armageddon grinds on, and one of the Black Templars' fighting companies has vanished into the planet's choking jungles. Marshal Brant leads a force to find his lost brothers, unaware that a band of Imperial ork-hunters is also out in the green hell, searching for a high-ranking officer downed in a crash. None of them realise what else stirs beneath the canopy: the savage greenskins of the Blood Scar tribe stalk them through the undergrowth, and something far older and darker is waking to reach out once more. What begins as a rescue becomes a fight on two fronts as the Templars uncover a corrupting plot and must face renegade Space Marines as well as the endless ork tide.",
